OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with some showery rain
OL,7,Fmoving eastwards. Then mainly dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells but a few showers
OL,9,Fcontinuing in the far north. Patchy
OL,10,Ffrost and ice possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA frost to start the day in
OL,13,Fsome places. Mostly dry with good
OL,14,Fspells of sunshine but some high cloud
OL,15,Fwill spread across at times. The odd
OL,16,Fshower in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
