OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright start on Wednesday but
OL,7,Fcloudier with outbreaks of rain later.
OL,8,FRain bands moving east on Thursday
OL,9,Ffollowed by drier, brighter spells for
OL,10,Fthe rest of the week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
